		<span class="icomoon icon-icon_tw"></span>
	</a>
	<a class="share-linkedin" href="https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.welivesecurity.com%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2Fcryptocurrency-exchange-hackers-bounty%2F" target="blank" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" data-original-title="Share on Linkedin">
